Trade/Device Name(s): Randox Maternal Controls Level 1, Level 2 and Level 3
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Randox Maternal Controls Levels 1, 2 and 3 used for quality control of Unconjugated Estriol and Total Beta Human Chorionic Gonadotrophin methods in clinical chemistry.
Indications for Use Summary: Intended for in vitro diagnostic use in the quality control of Unconjugated Estriol and Total Beta Human Chorionic Gonadotrophin methods on clinical chemistry systems.
